              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="3" width="18" height="14" rx="2" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M9 8l5 3-5 3V8Z" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="v2-course-cat">Pós-graduação</span>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-course-body">
            <h3>Descomplicando a Pós-Graduação</h3>
            <p>Estruture seu projeto, organize estudos e desenvolva pensamento científico desde os primeiros passos.</p>
            <div class="v2-course-footer">
              <span>Módulo introdutório</span>
              <a href="#" class="v2-link-arrow" style="font-size:13px;">Avise-me <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-course-card">
          <div class="v2-course-thumb v2-course-thumb--2">
            <img src="/assets/images/curso-metodologia.jpg" alt="Metodologia de Pesquisa" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
            <div class="v2-course-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none"><path d="M2 18 C4 18 5 10 8 10 C11 10 11 14 14 7 C17 0 18 5 20 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="v2-course-cat">Metodologia</span>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-course-body">
            <h3>Descomplicando a Metodologia de Pesquisa</h3>
            <p>Perguntas PICO, delineamentos e estrutura de estudos com rigor e lógica aplicada.</p>
            <div class="v2-course-footer">
              <span>Módulo avançado</span>
              <a href="#" class="v2-link-arrow" style="font-size:13px;">Avise-me <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-course-card">
          <div class="v2-course-thumb v2-course-thumb--3">
            <img src="/assets/images/curso-estatistica.jpg" alt="Estatística em Pesquisa" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
            <div class="v2-course-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none"><rect x="2" y="10" width="4" height="10" rx="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.5"/><rect x="9" y="6" width="4" height="14" rx="1" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7"/><rect x="16" y="2" width="4" height="18" rx="1" fill="currentColor"/></svg>
            </div>
            <span class="v2-course-cat">Estatística</span>
          </div>
          <div class="v2-course-body">
            <h3>Descomplicando a Estatística em Pesquisa</h3>
            <p>Do p-valor ao intervalo de confiança, com exemplos de estudos publicados no PubMed e SciELO.</p>
            <div class="v2-course-footer">
              <span>Módulo avançado</span>
              <a href="#" class="v2-link-arrow" style="font-size:13px;">Avise-me <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none"><path d="M1 7h12M8 3l4 4-4 4" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="v2-course-card">
          <div class="v2-course-thumb v2-course-thumb--4">
            <img src="/assets/images/curso-gbd.jpg" alt="GBD e Epidemiologia Global" loading="lazy" onerror="this.style.display='none'" />
            <div class="v2-course-placeholder" aria-hidden="true">
              <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 22 22" fill="none"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"/><path d="M2 11h18M11 2c-2 3-3 6-3 9s1 6 3 9M11 2c2 3 3 6 3 9s-1 6-3 9" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/></svg>
            </div>
